because for Me who is the other?

498
00:26:05,130 --> 00:26:08,663
When somebody is just a part and parcel of My being,

499
00:26:08,801 --> 00:26:11,460
itself my finger is paining; I’m just rubbing it

500
00:26:11,618 --> 00:26:13,424
and I must do it.

501
00:26:13,661 --> 00:26:16,610
For that I don’t have to awaken people; they just get it.

502
00:26:16,865 --> 00:26:19,047
You just stand near a person, you get a headache

503
00:26:19,228 --> 00:26:21,611
and you ask the person, “Have you got a headache?” “Yes.”

504
00:26:21,752 --> 00:26:24,206
You rub your head and rub his head and just finish it off.

505
00:26:24,307 --> 00:26:30,418
You just cannot help it because the macrocosm, the Viraat,

506
00:26:32,819 --> 00:26:37,219
informs you when you are one with it that, “see, the other fellow

507
00:26:37,660 --> 00:26:40,130
is suffering. ” You become that.

508
00:26:40,309 --> 00:26:43,803
You become collectively conscious. It is not a lecture or anything

509
00:26:43,905 --> 00:26:47,395
but it’s a becoming within you 
that you start feeling on your fingers,

510
00:26:47,554 --> 00:26:50,973
on your fingertips, what are the centers catching,

511
00:26:51,073 --> 00:26:52,731
what is the problem of the other person,

512
00:26:52,831 --> 00:26:56,263
how to cure it, what to do it. Everything, all this knowledge

513
00:26:56,363 --> 00:26:59,279
is given in Sahaja Yoga, absolutely free.

514
00:26:59,556 --> 00:27:01,869
Out of so many who are sitting here

515
00:27:02,010 --> 00:27:04,331
you can ask how many have been suffering from diseases

516
00:27:04,470 --> 00:27:06,029
have been cured completely,

517
00:27:06,168 --> 00:27:11,366
and since they have been realized 
not a single pie has been given to the doctors.

518
00:27:11,645 --> 00:27:15,176
It is not necessary to look after your health,

519
00:27:15,395 --> 00:27:18,092
not necessary to do much about it.

520
00:27:18,272 --> 00:27:20,592
We have had people who have had three heart attacks

521
00:27:20,732 --> 00:27:22,497
and now they are going strong.

522
00:27:22,696 --> 00:27:24,672
We have had people who had leukemia,

523
00:27:24,772 --> 00:27:26,577
who had all kinds of diseases. Today

524
00:27:26,656 --> 00:27:28,839
you won’t believe they ever had that disease

525
00:27:28,978 --> 00:27:32,378
because now the inside is completely into balance,

526
00:27:32,589 --> 00:27:36,894
integrated and blessed by God’s divine power within you.

527
00:27:37,252 --> 00:27:38,930
This is our heritage.

528
00:27:39,049 --> 00:27:40,279
We have to cash on it.

529
00:27:40,399 --> 00:27:42,958
And by this only we are going to remove the poverty,

530
00:27:43,077 --> 00:27:47,719
one day you will see, and not by patching up few things.

531
00:27:47,839 --> 00:27:51,410
I would request Mr. Vijay Merchant and we have another

532
00:27:51,569 --> 00:27:55,676
great social worker with us, is Gidubai Kotak,

533
00:27:55,815 --> 00:27:59,021
that you should pay little more attention to our Sahaja Yoga

534
00:27:59,156 --> 00:28:01,442
and see the dynamics of the Sahaja Yoga.

535
00:28:01,621 --> 00:28:05,291
You’ll be amazed how one person, the person who spoke to you

536
00:28:05,430 --> 00:28:08,496
just now, was from Rahuri, these two persons.

537
00:28:08,803 --> 00:28:11,918
They have given realization to ten thousands people.

538
00:28:12,077 --> 00:28:15,172
Just go and see their houses. Just go and see their children.

539
00:28:15,311 --> 00:28:17,671
They are bubbling with joy, with happiness,

540
00:28:17,831 --> 00:28:21,034
and you do not see any poverty in their hearts at all.

541
00:28:21,154 --> 00:28:23,892
Their hearts have been enriched and they are doing so well.

542
00:28:24,011 --> 00:28:25,915
Because the energy comes within you,

543
00:28:26,055 --> 00:28:28,534
the Saraswati tattwa is also enlightened

544
00:28:28,655 --> 00:28:31,253
and you start thinking as to what is to be done

545
00:28:31,372 --> 00:28:34,824
and how to, how to make your life happy.

546
00:28:35,003 --> 00:28:36,936
But money is not everything;

547
00:28:37,087 --> 00:28:40,353
food is not everything. Unless and until you get

548
00:28:40,569 --> 00:28:43,497
to know your Atma you can never be happy.

549
00:28:43,696 --> 00:28:46,672
So go to the roots and it’s so easy. You don’t have to pay anything

550
00:28:46,815 --> 00:28:48,993
You don’t have to have many organization, nothing.

551
00:28:49,113 --> 00:28:53,418
It just works, just like this. So why worry and why just

552
00:28:53,597 --> 00:28:55,530
think of something terrible?

553
00:28:55,640 --> 00:28:57,763
Now more we are ahead, talk to Gidubai also

554
00:28:57,922 --> 00:29:00,374
that they were enamored by one guru

555
00:29:00,553 --> 00:29:02,437
who were showing some miracles.

556
00:29:02,656 --> 00:29:05,692
And I, I had met somebody from Morvi

557
00:29:05,831 --> 00:29:06,854
who came to see Me,

558
00:29:06,974 --> 00:29:10,882
and I told him that you just 
don’t have anything to do with this horrible fellow,

559
00:29:11,044 --> 00:29:16,596
because a day will come when Kalki is 
at work and there will be destruction.

560
00:29:16,795 --> 00:29:18,473
He wouldn’t listen to Me.

561
00:29:18,712 --> 00:29:21,350
I went to Andhra. For your information I tell you

562
00:29:21,509 --> 00:29:26,909
I went to Andhra. I told to Andhra people that, 
“You don’t grow this tobacco.”

563
00:29:27,064 --> 00:29:29,797
In Andhra there are two types of people:

564
00:29:29,962 --> 00:29:32,699
one who are making lots of money; the other are the so-called poor

565
00:29:32,819 --> 00:29:34,664
who are doing lot of black magic.

566
00:29:34,992 --> 00:29:36,639
I talked to both of them.

567
00:29:36,779 --> 00:29:39,775
I told them, “Don’t do black magic because if you do black magic

568
00:29:39,894 --> 00:29:41,521
Lakshmi tattwa will disappear.”

569
00:29:41,640 --> 00:29:45,107
If the black magic comes from this side, 
the Lakshmi goes from the other side.

570
00:29:45,246 --> 00:29:47,032
And they just didn’t listen to Me.

571
00:29:47,175 --> 00:29:49,627
And I talked to these people who were growing tobacco.

572
00:29:49,726 --> 00:29:52,926
They wouldn’t listen. There are on three tapes,

573
00:29:53,715 --> 00:29:58,198
there is a lecture, where I said that the sea

574
00:29:58,695 --> 00:30:00,961
is the incarnation of Datattreya.

575
00:30:01,135 --> 00:30:04,091
It will take a respite, I, believe Me.

576
00:30:04,548 --> 00:30:07,081
And that’s what has happened with it.

577
00:30:07,246 --> 00:30:10,380
We have to understand that God knows all of us.

578
00:30:11,313 --> 00:30:13,476
He knows us in masses,

579
00:30:13,695 --> 00:30:15,828
and He knows where we are going

580
00:30:16,076 --> 00:30:17,609
and what we are doing.

581
00:30:17,822 --> 00:30:21,289
Your Bombay has escaped recently a very big drought.

582
00:30:21,892 --> 00:30:25,956
But please take heed and take to God.

583
00:30:26,194 --> 00:30:28,278
It is no question of going to Himalayas, of course,

584
00:30:28,397 --> 00:30:30,545
and no question of running away from it.

585
00:30:30,738 --> 00:30:32,793
But get it within yourself,

586
00:30:33,269 --> 00:30:36,424
try, as many as you can bring in here,

587
00:30:36,651 --> 00:30:40,769
if the saints are there. Those who are Sahaja Yogis are saints.

588
00:30:40,947 --> 00:30:45,907
Then God definitely will bless you, definitely will bless you.

589
00:30:46,205 --> 00:30:51,435
And the same people who are realized today 
have done tremendous work in the villages.

590
00:30:51,634 --> 00:30:55,225
They have emancipated so many villages without any money,

591
00:30:55,344 --> 00:30:58,201
without anything. When I go in the villages I’m really surprised

592
00:30:58,855 --> 00:31:04,610
how people get cured, how they are helped, how they get energetic,

593
00:31:04,868 --> 00:31:08,233
how they understand things. It’s most amazing.

594
00:31:08,431 --> 00:31:13,054
So the power of all the powers, that is the power of God’s Love,

595
00:31:13,293 --> 00:31:16,756
let us take to it. Let us take advantage of Him

596
00:31:16,906 --> 00:31:19,706
and leave everything in the hands of God.

597
00:31:19,872 --> 00:31:23,539
Only get Him into everyone you think who is suffering.

598
00:31:23,681 --> 00:31:27,252
You get Me hundred people who are suffering, I will see to them.

599
00:31:27,451 --> 00:31:30,479
Today if the whole hall was filled I would have cured all of them.

600
00:31:30,598 --> 00:31:32,840
You know that I have done it. It is not difficult.

601
00:31:32,959 --> 00:31:37,165
It is no boasting. It’s a fact. It’s a fact.

602
00:31:37,324 --> 00:31:41,224
It works in five minutes, for so many people can get it.

603
00:31:41,819 --> 00:31:44,518
But people do not want to face reality

604
00:31:44,716 --> 00:31:46,592
and they do not want to attend to it.

605
00:31:46,712 --> 00:31:49,311
Now we have already so many Sahaja Yogis in Bombay.

606
00:31:49,410 --> 00:31:51,783
So you can imagine I’ve worked here for nine years.

607
00:31:51,902 --> 00:31:53,926
We have some more of course in the outer centers

608
00:31:54,045 --> 00:31:56,704
but here in the center we have so many or little more.

609
00:31:57,002 --> 00:31:59,068
So you can see how people are.

