00:31:59,204 --> 00:32:02,676
And the work you are doing from outside,

611
00:32:02,855 --> 00:32:08,172
it’s all like a blind person going doing 
this work, that work, that work, that work.

612
00:32:08,351 --> 00:32:10,811
Politicians also think they are doing great work.

613
00:32:10,969 --> 00:32:12,250
All right, they are doing.

