00:32:12,351 --> 00:32:14,255
Social workers are also doing great work.

615
00:32:14,404 --> 00:32:16,854
Everybody’s doing. But there’s no coordination,

616
00:32:16,974 --> 00:32:19,831
there’s no integration and there’s no satisfaction

617
00:32:19,950 --> 00:32:22,350
of what one is doing. The reason is

618
00:32:22,490 --> 00:32:24,327
all of them belong to the one whole

619
00:32:24,532 --> 00:32:26,549
and they have not yet connected with the whole,

620
00:32:26,688 --> 00:32:29,465
which one has to do. We are finding our wholesomeness

621
00:32:29,565 --> 00:32:32,858
all over the world, whether we are Indians, Americans or anything.

622
00:32:32,978 --> 00:32:35,537
We are all just trying to find out our wholesomeness,

623
00:32:35,716 --> 00:32:38,036
and the answer is Sahaja Yoga.

624
00:32:39,347 --> 00:32:42,213
It is Sahaja Yoga. There’s no other answer

625
00:32:42,341 --> 00:32:45,157
to anyone of these problems. Today I am telling you,

626
00:32:45,277 --> 00:32:47,544
again you can tell Me afterwards.

627
00:32:47,653 --> 00:32:48,934
You give Me your problems.

628
00:32:49,054 --> 00:32:51,137
You tell Me who are the downtrodden. Let Me see.

629
00:32:51,276 --> 00:32:52,922
Let Me see who are the downtrodden.

630
00:32:53,042 --> 00:32:55,323
Now you, somebody wanted Me to go and see the fishermen.

631
00:32:55,463 --> 00:32:57,188
I said, “All right, I’ll go and see them.”

632
00:32:57,308 --> 00:32:59,490
I’m sure if I, they get realization,

633
00:32:59,669 --> 00:33:03,002
their fishery will improve, definitely, 
hundred per cent; I’m sure of it.

634
00:33:03,577 --> 00:33:07,177
Everything improves because God’s blessings are there

635
00:33:07,328 --> 00:33:11,409
and God has got the six qualities which makes Him Bhagwan.

636
00:33:11,588 --> 00:33:15,521
It’s one of them is Shubha, Auspicious. Another is Kalyan.

637
00:33:15,972 --> 00:33:18,056
Another is Aishwary [GW: Ishwari?].

638
00:33:18,354 --> 00:33:20,821
Like these the six qualities of God.

639
00:33:21,052 --> 00:33:23,786
These six qualities emit from the being,

640
00:33:24,048 --> 00:33:26,500
and once you face it you get it.

641
00:33:26,679 --> 00:33:28,213
You want to do Kalyan;

642
00:33:28,306 --> 00:33:30,072
all right, then face people to God,

643
00:33:30,171 --> 00:33:32,433
and this is the way by which you can face it.

644
00:33:32,552 --> 00:33:35,707
You don’t have to organize churches and temples or anything.

645
00:33:35,806 --> 00:33:41,284
It’s just the energy which has to flow, Shakti that has to flow.

646
00:33:41,444 --> 00:33:44,977
Like you can see a wood is lying there, has nothing.

647
00:33:45,214 --> 00:33:48,700
But if you enlighten it, it gives you light, fire, everything.

648
00:33:48,859 --> 00:33:50,637
In the same way enlightenment

649
00:33:50,816 --> 00:33:52,899
is the only way to solve the problem,

650
00:33:53,018 --> 00:33:57,418
and all of us should try to enlighten as many people as possible.

651
00:33:57,681 --> 00:34:03,216
Our work, of course, is more for 
the middle class because the extremes do not take to us.

652
00:34:03,415 --> 00:34:05,498
But when the middle course increases,

653
00:34:05,637 --> 00:34:07,263
