00:34:07,383 --> 00:34:09,010
She can feed on the both the sides.

655
00:34:09,129 --> 00:34:11,906
Gradually the both the sides can also join [them],

656
00:34:12,045 --> 00:34:14,656
but the depth is in the center, in the madhya marga,

657
00:34:14,815 --> 00:34:16,223
and there it works out.

