00:34:22,810 --> 00:34:25,529
and they have the blessings necessary

662
00:34:25,645 --> 00:34:27,335
because they lead a very normal life.

663
00:34:27,474 --> 00:34:29,272
Once they learn their swimming

664
00:34:29,404 --> 00:34:31,494
they must know themselves before helping others.

665
00:34:31,673 --> 00:34:34,391
You must help yourself, you must become yourself,

