679
00:35:05,506 --> 00:35:08,240
So this is what is a very dynamic force.

680
00:35:08,384 --> 00:35:10,348
I would request all the social workers

681
00:35:10,507 --> 00:35:13,707
to open their eyes to this tremendous discovery

682
00:35:13,860 --> 00:35:15,308
that has come to our country

683
00:35:15,448 --> 00:35:18,706
and to see for themselves what it is like, what it means.

684
00:35:18,865 --> 00:35:22,924
It transforms a personality into such a dynamic web

685
00:35:23,063 --> 00:35:26,796
that an ordinary boy can become a great cricket player.

686
00:35:27,348 --> 00:35:30,681
An ordinary musician can become a great musician.

687
00:35:30,920 --> 00:35:36,495
An ordinarily dull boy can become a first class student.

688
00:35:36,651 --> 00:35:37,784
It has happened.

689
00:35:37,944 --> 00:35:41,423
There are many who will say it has happen in their cases.

690
00:35:41,602 --> 00:35:43,815
So many things have happen like this,

691
00:35:44,015 --> 00:35:48,181
and so we have to depend on the mercy of God for this.

692
00:35:48,400 --> 00:35:51,455
Only thing is we have to desire and ask for it.

693
00:35:51,614 --> 00:35:54,014
I think, the other day I had a talk

694
00:35:54,154 --> 00:35:58,955
with one of the political leaders. I said, 
