696
00:36:03,597 --> 00:36:06,589
Without adhyatma, without the Atma in it,

697
00:36:06,788 --> 00:36:09,685
without the Spirit of God in it, you are doing it

698
00:36:09,845 --> 00:36:12,027
because in you something is dying,

699
00:36:12,186 --> 00:36:15,986
in you something is feeling, that what is feeling in you

700
00:36:16,690 --> 00:36:18,424
is the part of the whole.

701
00:36:18,595 --> 00:36:21,529
So know the whole and you’ll be so dynamic.

702
00:36:21,770 --> 00:36:25,636
You’ll be so great and the whole thing will flow from you

703
00:36:25,812 --> 00:36:28,812
and you can really help thousands of people.

